*Onih* ljudi su bili veoma uspešni. (Those people were very successful.)

*Njihovih* uspeha nismo bili svesni. (We were not aware of their successes.)

Niko nije mogao da zaboravi *onih* dana. (Nobody could forget those days.)

Ona je još uvek sanjala *njihove* snove. (She was still dreaming their dreams.)

*Njihova* ljubav je bila neizmerna. (Their love was immeasurable.)

Mnogi su se nadali *onim* rečima. (Many hoped for those words.)